repository-code: "https://github.com/OthmanAdi/plan-it"
url: "https://github.com/OthmanAdi/plan-it"
abstract: >
  plan-it is a Claude Code skill that produces a single self-contained
  HTML plan with embedded JSON state, interactive controls (drag-and-drop,
  sliders, copy-as-markdown), and survives /clear via IDE session catchup.
  It is the successor format to planning-with-files, built for the
  HTML-as-control-surface paradigm Anthropic engineer Thariq Shihipar
  introduced in "The Unreasonable Effectiveness of HTML" (2026-05-08).
keywords:
